publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-1577 Phil Gallie: Princess Anne's Visit to Gibraltar-That the Parliament commends Princess Anne's welcome and successful visit to Gibraltar in June 2004 and urges the First Minister, in his role as a Privy Councillor, to encourage Her Majesty the Queen to visit Gibraltar for the first time since her visit of 50 years ago.
S2M-1577 Princess Anne's Visit to Gibraltar (lodged on 9 July 2004) Alex Johnstone*, Murdo Fraser*, Mr David Davidson*, John Scott*, Mr Brian Monteith*, Bill Aitken*, Mr Ted Brocklebank*
